{"tid":1380974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港文化傳統] 搭棚技術","createTime":"2019-07-29T06:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T07:04:45.000Z","uid":22924,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2f3c5577b5540073204a0d439a35bb27c3626858","tid":1380974,"uid":22924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:43:29.000Z","msg":"眼見最近有人拿到唔少竹但都當垃圾掉落地下<br />\n特此宣傳下香港既文化傳統 -- 搭棚技術<br />\n當技術熟練時，要搭有相當體積既結構需時只要十至十五分鐘即可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本材料:<br />\n1.  篾仔<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.waiyan.edu.hk/ICH/subjects/comp/03/web/new_page_12.files/image001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.waiyan.edu.hk%2FICH%2Fsubjects%2Fcomp%2F03%2Fweb%2Fnew_page_12.files%2Fimage001.jpg&h=49444f56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.  竹 (普遍拿到都係約6米 ~ 9米)<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.waiyan.edu.hk/ICH/subjects/comp/03/web/new_page_12.files/image003.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.waiyan.edu.hk%2FICH%2Fsubjects%2Fcomp%2F03%2Fweb%2Fnew_page_12.files%2Fimage003.jpg&h=0b61482b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3.  鋸 (用來鋸竹至更短既長度，未必有此需要) <br />\n<img src=\"https://shop.r10s.jp/honmamon-r/cabinet/img4/w1111945.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.r10s.jp%2Fhonmamon-r%2Fcabinet%2Fimg4%2Fw1111945.jpg&h=9a2b8522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紮竹技巧:<br />\n傳統紮竹技巧係唔需要打結，只單靠篾仔自身不停打轉產生既摩擦力<br />\n所以技術熟練時係會比膠索帶紮得更快, 更穩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可留意以下YOUTUBE 片段 為基本紮竹技巧 (1:35 開始)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yY84E4dFsWw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyY84E4dFsWw&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67UzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=8d641caf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yY84E4dFsWw</a>"},{"pid":"6a59d57b38a59e5a6a343f9f279c3cea7b010052","tid":1380974,"uid":22924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f345e582ef9f7fdd6480da9adfa0bd5c52555b05","tid":1380974,"uid":195485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:49:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"863a8536d9efa583743ea43c6a33a1100543a817","tid":1380974,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:50:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推! 8月5罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"1208003b454f77c374302053d5166fd2b702117a","tid":1380974,"uid":22924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}